Swiss running shoe brand On Holding $ONON plans to raise $600M at a $6B market cap. On is a global provider of premium athletic footwear, apparel, and accessories that are designed using sustainable materials and its proprietary technology.

On Holding $ONON is a niche DTC brand with Roger Federer as an investor. Their shoes are great, growth is strong and they are profitable but the valuation is pretty crazy at 9x sales and 63x EBITDA. The current range is $18-20.
The question in my mind is whether or not $ONON closes tomorrow with an enterprise value greater than $UAA...
